documentation:
JSON formatter.

Shape of the JSON output:

```json
{
    "evaluables": {
        "model_foo": {
            "score": 5.0,
            "badge": "🥈",
            "pass": true,
            "results": {
                "rule1": {
                    "result": "OK",
                    "severity": null
                    "message": null
                },
                "rule2": {
                    "result": "WARN",
                    "severity": "medium",
                    "message": "Model lacks a description."
                }
            ]
        },
        "model_bar": {
            "score": 0.0,
            "badge": "🥉",
            "pass": false,
            "results": {
                "rule1": {
                    "result": "ERR",
                    "message": "Exception message"
                }
            }
        }
    },
    "project": {
        "score": 2.5,
        "badge": "🥉",
        "pass": false
    }
}
```
